{
  "stem": "150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were searching through the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've hid-- I hid in latrine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't find me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the kids were taken away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After the war, I found out that they were taken to where Mengele was performing experiments and that most of them died.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of them survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, to my amazement, I just read an article by somebody, a young man who appeared-- a kid who was part of the group and did manage to survive and apparently was still in his right mind.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know there were any.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I stayed behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the thing is, you see, that even though I was only 13, there weren't supposed to be any kids left.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the kids were taken away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the commandant's responsibility that there were no kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So obviously, if they found a 13-year-old kid, it would be a black mark against him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So naturally, officially I became 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody you know-- of course, the more elegant solution, which obviously didn't occur to him, was to shoot me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he didn't think of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So instead he made me 18, and I had the same rights and privileges as everybody else, and me and the other four or five kids.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The work we did-- at first, I was very, very lucky because some of the Jews within the camp, you know, who were in positions of authority from Lithuania, they knew me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got a job inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my job at first-- my first job, was cleaning latrines, which sounds disgusting, but actually it was very good because these boards with big holes in them and all that.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
